			central_monitor: But can it run Doom?
			charcoal_pile: Underground fuel bakery
			charcoal_pile_0: Turns Logs into [c/55FF55:Charcoal][c/AAAAAA: when ][c/FF5555:ignited][c/AAAAAA:.]
			charcoal_pile_1: Right Click with fire-starting items to start.
			charcoal_pile_2: Pyrolysis occurs in up to a [c/55FFFF:9x4x9][c/AAAAAA: space beneath.]
			charcoal_pile_3: Logs must be not be exposed to [c/FFFF55:Air][c/AAAAAA:!]
			cleanroom: Keeping those pesky particles out
			cleanroom_0: Place machines inside to run cleanroom recipes.
			cleanroom_1: Uses [c/FFFFFF:30 EU/t][c/AAAAAA: when dirty, ][c/FFFFFF:4 EU/t][c/AAAAAA: when clean.]
			cleanroom_2: Overclocking increases cleaning per cycle.
			cleanroom_3: "[c/55FFFF:Size: ][c/FFFFFF:5x5x5 to 15x15x15]"
			cleanroom_4: Requires [c/FFFFFF:Filter Casings ][c/AAAAAA:in the ceiling, excluding the edges.]
			cleanroom_5: Accepts up to [c/FFFFFF:4 Doors][c/AAAAAA:! Remains clean when the door is open.]
			cleanroom_6: Generators, Mufflers, Drills, and Primitive Machines are too dirty for the cleanroom!
			cleanroom_7: Send power through [c/FFFFFF:Hulls ][c/AAAAAA:or ][c/FFFFFF:Diodes ][c/AAAAAA:in the walls.]
			coke_oven: Making better fuels for Steel and Power
